{% comment %} Bespoke content for the Luma Classic Mattress product — layer diagram, comfort
   scale, feature cards, comparison table, testimonial, size guide, FAQ. Ported verbatim
   from luma.html. Rendered by sections/main-product.liquid via two parts: 'spec' (inside
   the buy panel) and 'body' (the "Inside the Luma" section onward). {% endcomment %}

{% case part %}

{% when 'spec' %}
    <div class="spec-mini">
        <div><b>Thickness</b>6"</div>
        <div><b>Comfort Scale</b>Medium</div>
        <div><b>Best for</b>Combination sleepers, daily comfort seekers</div>
    </div>

{% when 'body' %}
    <section class="story section--dark">
        <blockquote>Obsessed with mattresses, <em>so you can be obsessed with sleep.</em></blockquote>
        <p>Every Luma Classic fuses traditional craftsmanship with innovative foam technology — certified foams, precision quilting, and a layer stack we've refined year after year, backed by a 7-year warranty.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="inside">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal" style="margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;max-width:620px;margin-left:0;">
                <h2>Seven layers of engineered comfort</h2>
                <p>Tap a layer to see what it does. Pro Nexa Foam and a Hybrid Pocket Spring core give the Luma range its signature adaptive bounce.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="layers-grid">
                <svg class="layer-svg" viewBox="0 0 520 424" role="img" aria-label="Cross-section of the Luma Classic mattress showing seven layers">
                    <g id="slabA" class="slab" data-layer="A">
                        <path d="M30 44 Q30 22 66 22 L454 22 Q490 22 490 44 L490 58 L30 58 Z" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M56 36 q13 -6 26 0 M102 36 q13 -6 26 0 M148 36 q13 -6 26 0 M194 36 q13 -6 26 0 M240 36 q13 -6 26 0 M286 36 q13 -6 26 0 M332 36 q13 -6 26 0 M378 36 q13 -6 26 0 M424 36 q13 -6 26 0" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
                        <text x="12" y="46">A</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabB" class="slab" data-layer="B">
                        <rect x="30" y="62" width="460" height="40" fill="#E4F2C5" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M50 82 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12 l20 -12 l20 12" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
                        <text x="12" y="88">B</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabC" class="slab" data-layer="C">
                        <rect x="30" y="106" width="460" height="46" fill="#E4F2C5" stroke="#3F5E12" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <text x="12" y="135">C</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabD" class="slab" data-layer="D">
                        <rect x="30" y="156" width="460" height="46" fill="#F2F4EC" stroke="#3F5E12" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <text x="12" y="185">D</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabE" class="slab" data-layer="E">
                        <rect x="30" y="206" width="460" height="50" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#9D9E9E" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <g stroke="#6B6B6B" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none" opacity=".6">
                            <circle cx="80" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="150" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="220" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="290" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="360" cy="231" r="9"/><circle cx="430" cy="231" r="9"/>
                        </g>
                        <text x="12" y="237">E</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabF" class="slab" data-layer="F">
                        <rect x="30" y="260" width="460" height="76" fill="#3F5E12" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <g stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" opacity=".8">
                            <path d="M70 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M140 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M210 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M280 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M350 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26 M420 272 q-9 13 0 26 q9 13 0 26"/>
                        </g>
                        <text x="12" y="304" fill="#FEFEFE">F</text>
                    </g>
                    <g id="slabG" class="slab" data-layer="G">
                        <path d="M30 340 L490 340 L490 364 Q490 388 450 388 L70 388 Q30 388 30 364 Z" fill="#F6F8F1" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M60 366 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10 l16 -10 l16 10" stroke="#95C12B" stroke-width="1.1" fill="none" opacity=".6"/>
                        <text x="12" y="370">G</text>
                    </g>
                </svg>

                <div id="layerList">
                    <div class="layer-item active" data-layer="A" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">A.</span> Super Plush Luxeknit Fabric</h3>
                        <p>Premium stretch-knit fabric offering breathability, durability, and a luxurious soft touch.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="B" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">B.</span> Aeroflex Foam Quilting</h3>
                        <p>Cushioned comfort layer offering enhanced softness and gentle contouring support.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="C" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">C.</span> Pro Nexa Foam</h3>
                        <p>Lightweight stability with orthopaedic base support.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="D" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">D.</span> Vector Base Felt</h3>
                        <p>High-density felt providing structural stability, load distribution, and long-lasting mattress durability.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="E" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">E.</span> Hybrid Pocket Spring</h3>
                        <p>Individually pocketed springs offering targeted support, motion isolation, and breathable comfort.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="F" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">F.</span> Vector Base Felt</h3>
                        <p>High-density felt beneath the spring core, adding further structural stability and durability.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="G" tabindex="0" role="button">
                        <h3><span class="letter">G.</span> Soft Foam with Quilting</h3>
                        <p>Additional cushioning for enhanced comfort and a cozy sleeping experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="firmness">
                <h3>Where the Luma Classic sits on our comfort scale</h3>
                <div class="scale"><div class="scale-marker" style="left:50%;" title="Medium"></div></div>
                <div class="scale-labels"><span>Ultra plush</span><b>Luma Classic — medium</b><span>Extra firm</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--paper">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal">
                <h2>Deep, undisturbed sleep — by design</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-cards">
                <article class="fcard reveal" style="transition-delay:0ms;">
                    <div class="fcard-media"><img src="{{ 'product-luma-angle2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Close-up of the Luma's Luxeknit cover fabric" loading="lazy"></div>
                    <div class="fcard-body">
                        <h3>Luxeknit Breathability</h3>
                        <p>A precision stretch-knit cover that circulates air all night, so the mattress never traps heat.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="fcard reveal" style="transition-delay:80ms;">
                    <div class="fcard-media"><img src="{{ 'product-luma-angle3.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Side profile of the Luma Classic showing its layered construction" loading="lazy"></div>
                    <div class="fcard-body">
                        <h3>Hybrid Pocket Spring Core</h3>
                        <p>Individually pocketed coils add responsive bounce and motion isolation beneath the comfort foams — a feel neither Sova nor Ultima offers.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="fcard reveal" style="transition-delay:160ms;">
                    <div class="fcard-media"><img src="{{ 'product-luma-angle4.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="Front view of the Luma Classic mattress" loading="lazy"></div>
                    <div class="fcard-body">
                        <h3>Everyday Comfort Zone</h3>
                        <p>Aeroflex quilting and Pro Nexa foam blend into a balanced medium feel built for daily, uninterrupted sleep.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="compare">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal">
                <h2>Which Luma is yours?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="table-scroll">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr><th>Feature</th><th class="hl">Classic</th><th>Premium</th><th>Luxury</th></tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr><th>Top Fabric</th><td class="hl">Super Plush Luxeknit Fabric</td><td>Super Plush Luxeknit Fabric</td><td>Super Plush Luxeknit Fabric</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Comfort Layer</th><td class="hl">Aeroflex Foam Quilting</td><td>Aeroflex Foam Quilting</td><td>Aeroflex Foam Quilting</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Body Support</th><td class="hl">Pro Nexa Foam</td><td>Pro Nexa Foam</td><td>Memorest Foam + Pro Nexa Foam</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Main Support</th><td class="hl">Hybrid Pocket Spring</td><td>Hybrid Pocket Spring</td><td>Hybrid Pocket Spring</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Bottom Layer</th><td class="hl">Vector Base Felt + Soft Foam</td><td>Vector Base Felt + Soft Foam</td><td>Vector Base Felt + Soft Foam</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Thickness</th><td class="hl">6"</td><td>8"</td><td>10"</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Comfort Scale</th><td class="hl">Medium</td><td>Medium</td><td>Medium Soft</td></tr>
                        <tr><th>Warranty</th><td class="hl">7 Years + 5 Years Full Replacement*</td><td>7 Years + 5 Years Full Replacement*</td><td>7 Years + 5 Years Full Replacement*</td></tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p class="compare-note">*As per Foamico warranty terms. Not sure which one to pick? Visit our store to try them in person.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section--paper">
        <div class="wrap" style="text-align:center;">
            <span class="stars reveal" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
            <div class="quote-banner reveal" style="margin-top:16px;">
                <blockquote>"Luma is the first mattress that felt right for both of us — I like it soft, my partner likes it firm, and somehow this just works for both."</blockquote>
                <cite>— Verified buyer, New Delhi</cite>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    {% render 'size-guide', product: product %}

    <section class="section section--paper" id="faq">
        <div class="wrap">
            <div class="section-head reveal">
                <h2>Mattress FAQs</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What makes Luma different from Sova and Ultima?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Luma is built for everyday, all-round comfort — a Medium feel with a Hybrid Pocket Spring core that adds bounce and airflow the all-foam Sova and Ultima ranges don't have.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Is Luma too soft for back support?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>No — support and softness live in different layers. The Aeroflex quilting and Pro Nexa foam give you the cushioned feel, while the Hybrid Pocket Spring core and Vector Base Felt layers keep your spine aligned.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Will it sleep hot?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>The Luxeknit stretch fabric plus the pocket spring core, which allows airflow between coils, keep the sleep surface breathable all night.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What does the warranty cover?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Every Luma comes with a 7-year warranty, including 5 years of full replacement*, covering manufacturing defects under normal use. Full terms are available from our team.</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Can I try it before buying?<span class="plus">+</span></button>
                    <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — visit our store in Ghitorni, New Delhi to try the full Luma range in person, or call us at +91 74969 82886 (Mon–Sat, 9 AM–6 PM) and our sleep experts will help you choose.</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

{% endcase %}
